        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>Omnia in Amore was born from a passion for creating heartfelt crafts that celebrate life's special moments. Every item is crafted with sustainability in mind, using ethically sourced materials to ensure beauty with a purpose.</p>
        <p>Crafting became a significant part of my life in 2023 after the loss of a close loved one. I found myself crafting all hours of the day and night to keep my mind occupied. It brought peace, and through this hobby, Omnia in Amore was created to share that joy with others.</p>
